<!-- TEMPLATE PAGE -->

<div class="content-col clearfix">

    <!-- IMAGE FRAME DOESN'T CHANGE EXCEPT FOR BACKGROUND IMG -->
    <div class="frame-container clearfix">
        <div class="image-frame">
            <div class="stats-bar clearfix">
                <div class="stat-35">
                    Capt Log<br>
                    OT-00<span class="idSpan">{{items.captain_id}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 prof">
                    <img height="13px" src="/images/prof_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.proficiency_points}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-prof">Proficiency</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 scrap">
                    <img height="12px" src="/images/scrap_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.scrap_amount}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-scrap">Scrap</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-20 crew">
                    <img height="12px" src="/images/crew_icon.svg">
                    <span>{{items.crew_hp}}</span>
                    <div class="stat-text hide-crew">Crew</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="image-box" style="background-image: url('../images/storyimg/3_1.png');"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="frame-container clearfix">
        <div class="text-frame">
            <div class="text-title">
                Planet Class M
            </div>
            <div class="text-divide"></div>
            <div class="text-body">
                As you approach the second planet, you see it's bustling with activity - communications satellites with plenty of radio activity. The planet below looks covered in water with a thin and clear atmosphere.
                <br />
                <br />
                The terminal beeps as you recieve a communication from the planet. "Greetings interstellar traveller! How may we help you?"
            </div>
            <div class="text-divide"></div>

            <!-- CHANGE DATA-ATTRIBUTES FOR EACH CHOICE // CHANGE DATA-CHAP/DATA-PAGE TO THE NEXT PAGE (SAME FOR EACH BUTTON) -->
            <div data-scrap="-25" data-crew="1" data-prof="10" data-chap="3" data-page="1a" class="option-buttons">
                "We would like to engage in commerce."
            </div>
            <div data-scrap="-5" data-crew="5" data-prof="3" data-chap="3" data-page="1b" class="option-buttons">
                "Are you open for cultural/scientific exchange?”
            </div>
            <div data-scrap="0" data-crew="0" data-prof="-1" data-chap="3" data-page="1c" class="option-buttons">
               "Whoa, you guys are ugly.” Close communications
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

